room_title: Escape room "Apartment 13" by Break Through Reno in Reno
room_address: 294 E. Moana Ln, Suite 13, Reno, NV 89502
room_description:
1445 Hunter St. is an old building with a dark history full of death and tragedy. Your little brother has gone missing. The investigators have not been much of a help and you take measures into your own hands. You go to the last known location your brother went to, 1445 Hunter St. Apartment 13.
No one is home and in your desperation, you decide to pick the lock and look for any clues. What is this place? You had no idea what you got yourself into! Escape before you become a part of this building's dark history!
